title: FC Jõgeva Wolves
text: FC Jõgeva Wolves is an <a href="Estonia">Estonia</a>n <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="J%C3%B5geva">Jõgeva</a>. Founded in 2014, they currently play in the <a href="II%20liiga">II liiga</a>, the fifth tier of Estonian football. Jõgeva Wolves also has reserve teams: FC Äksi Wolves, who play in the <a href="III%20liiga">III liiga</a> and FC Tallinna Wolves, who play in the <a href="IV%20liiga">IV liiga</a>.
